Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前好像遇到過同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我還認得它們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,片名：夜來了（3）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為了讓我們HIKARI 的世界「真夜」在世上實現...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 傳說創造新月出現的 原因的夜之女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓言靈使來喚出她的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺探出條件是唯一的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在使用那個男人的計劃中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來使可以輕易帶出 言靈使少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的言靈使真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為火蛇（KASHYA）的同伴 是一大誤算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不認為火蛇的力量 足以阻止「界」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座塔原本是建造來 讓我們獲得力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法得到言靈使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是無法讓「真夜」實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再給你一次機會 知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請去監視總司的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 為什麼這麼魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了總司的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續打倒HIKARI的話 哥哥一定會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須阻止哥哥個 一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我來幫忙你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒必要自己一個人 深夜在外遊逛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做這種自殘式的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想贖罪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你內疚自己 抹消了大家的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後悔對葉村和京華 下了他們是情侶的暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 誠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時不要管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在這裡等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想早點跟你見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷吧 快進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我暖和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的時候 我一直想與你這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答應我吧 阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個感覺是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有哪裡不對呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脈動著耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大... 你想做什麼呢 阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒聽見哦 明白講出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想用力的放進你裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿涼 我快壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你射在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢裡有個一臉兇惡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著刀追殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為什麼 我喊她姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我快被殺死時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿著黑衣服的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由空而降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以可怕的表情瞪著我講
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是背叛姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺騙我的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必須贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是夢 你不是什麼罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能時雨聲太大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害你做了奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再睡一會兒好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京華說的「不記得」的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才不知道為什麼我覺得自己一定要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對著怪物時 我也察覺到 自己遺忘了某種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京華來這房間一個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是在哪裡 在什麼時候認識的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我必須溫柔愛護她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對京華要溫柔一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不是故意裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被抹消記憶的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開她！哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的計劃裡面需要言靈使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要幫助HIKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把人們拉進無止境的夢中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無止境的夢中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 你也跟火蛇之裡的老人們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們隱約感到 HIKARI的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻沒有思考對策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然安穩的過日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為這種情況 稱得上是現實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓天文部的同伴們做的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與HIKARI讓人做的夢 有什麼不同嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人的罪業中 有魔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能理解到這點的 火蛇之裡的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就有偏差了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 人要受到懲罰才會安心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承受永遠的煉獄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事想問我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 你這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你是哪裡的傳教士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像是火蛇之裡的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 一直隱瞞我們這件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為沒有人問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前陣子火蛇之裡的隊長 小泉是你的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼說明這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一點 對我來說也是在預料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來要叫你別刺探 是很難了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總司 你到底在打什麼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制裁之日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木神！木神！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦???
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木神！木神會死掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木神會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶被抹消了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上喊人來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顧那個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我以外 她無法依靠別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我只是路人 你為什麼要拜託我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是可以信賴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是我們對戰過的火蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火蛇？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木神！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說 大家都想不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 這跟你沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去記憶的日子 不是比較快樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看寰海那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有阿涼與京華 他們不是在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你自己呢 為什麼一直纏著我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是HIKARI嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以回去同伴身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡太陰沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木神又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起去旅館 作愛怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉村涼 我有事找你談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 星川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們真的不知HIKARI與火蛇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為們的記憶 被封印起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈美被那些傢伙 擄走了呀 阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩確實可憐 可是我幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光是保護京華 就已經很勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京華 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼疼愛他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道連他你都忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准你碰京華！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿涼 你這麼想保護京華
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是受到社長的暗示呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎麼說 大家都不會想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 這跟你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫助人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道讓天文社的所有人 恢復記憶的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:19:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到平時冷酷的你 會這麼熱心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看到 京華不像京華的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長變得不像社長 真奈美變得不像真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木神那傢伙啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們的計劃接近完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿月夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言靈使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有條件都齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火蛇們就快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為這美好的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再增加一項樂子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在...賜給我那個力量....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以救出真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒哥哥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿涼 京華 誠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你們幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京華 你跑去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找你好久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了原來以前都是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有總司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總司也來啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破壞了你的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我們三個人一起去廟會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背叛美裡是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和你這麼做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受的話就不會有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墮落的話 不安就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊還沒經驗過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作戰的對象是HIKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被消除了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白 你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京華 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京華
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 抱歉這麼晚打攪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離家出走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛剛才補習完
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經過這裡時 突然想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 一個人在家有點怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.19,0:24:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉真的獨自去那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 你想一個人偷跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.67,0:24:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星川
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太見外了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能只讓學長當英雄的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.61,0:24:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉那個傻瓜 太會給人帶來麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.48,0:24:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.88,0:24:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣大家都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.09,0:24:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.29,0:24:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救真奈美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.70,0:25:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.30,0:25:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.11,0:25:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.17,0:25:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 小泉 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.98,0:25:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.91,0:25:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.85,0:25:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.06,0:25:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗黑獸貝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.46,0:25:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你們會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.73,0:25:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是好同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.73,0:25:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓你一個人背起 跟HIKARI的戰爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.67,0:25:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.80,0:25:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然對不起小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.40,0:25:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我還是解除了他們的暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.67,0:25:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 讓我們解決總司的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.15,0:25:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能答應
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.01,0:25:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼別怪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.69,0:25:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了可以活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.69,0:26:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們決定請你暫時休養一下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.62,0:26:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉村 剩下的交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.56,0:26:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等她醒來以後 再追上我們
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.43,0:26:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.63,0:26:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你那眼神是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.11,0:26:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算跟你有過那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.37,0:26:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們之間本來就沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.91,0:26:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到被這種人以男友自居 真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.85,0:26:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都厭惡自己
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.52,0:26:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.59,0:26:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼道歉啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.06,0:26:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.79,0:26:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了 葉村
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.26,0:26:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 這次的騎士讓給你做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.93,0:26:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好做哦 阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.80,0:26:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.94,0:26:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.27,0:26:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那麼在意我 讓我有點高興
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.41,0:26:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事 總司
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.88,0:27:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼夜之女王不出現
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.29,0:27:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說女王是 抱著怨恨之心離開這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.83,0:27:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個言靈使 可能少了一些怨恨的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓塔聚集的HIKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.90,0:27:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配合言靈使的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.90,0:27:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對著新月發射 你看怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.37,0:27:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新月是掛在夜空中 的另一個影子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.24,0:27:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新月本身充滿光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.65,0:27:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成沒有影子的世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.65,0:27:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HIKARI就無法棲息在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.62,0:28:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新月...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.55,0:28:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生麼什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.89,0:28:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待續